N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 210.6 - Standing room or roll tickets

State Regulations

No standing room, seating or roll tickets shall be sold for
any contest or exhibition in an amount resulting in attendance exceeding the
authorized capacity of the venue in which the match or exhibition takes
place. Notes
